<p class=\\"bb_p align_center\\"><img class="post_img" src="/uploads/images/2020-01-09/2020-01-09_06-03-10_447.png" alt="" title="" /></p><div class="source"><p class=\\"bb_p align_right\\"><a rel="nofollow noreferrer" href="https://ukr.media/science/408794/" target="_blank">За матеріалами "ukr.media"</a></p></div>',
